---
title: Beyond Meat® Burrito Bowls with Pico De Gallo and Green Onion Rice
description: Tasty Beyond Meat® takes centre stage, with green onion and lime rice as its co-star in this delicious dish. The fresh DIY pico de gallo makes a great extra!
